{
  "$comment": [
    "Adversarial temporal fixtures for cross-language parity tests.",
    "Each entry is a (scheduledLocal, iana) input plus the expected",
    "ComputeNextFire UTC instant. Both languages must produce IDENTICAL",
    "expectedUtc under NodaTime's LenientResolver (.NET) and Temporal's",
    "disambiguation:'compatible' (TS). If the two engines ever diverge on",
    "any fixture, the divergence must be surfaced + acknowledged — DO NOT",
    "silently adjust expectedUtc."
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "fixtures": [
    {
      "id": "us-spring-forward-skipped-2-30",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-03-08T02:30:00",
      "iana": "America/New_York",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-03-08T07:30:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "us-fall-back-ambiguous-1-30-picks-earlier",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-11-01T01:30:00",
      "iana": "America/New_York",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-11-01T05:30:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "european-spring-forward-skipped",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-03-29T01:30:00",
      "iana": "Europe/London",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-03-29T01:30:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "european-fall-back-ambiguous-picks-earlier",
      "scheduledLocal": "2025-10-26T01:30:00",
      "iana": "Europe/London",
      "expectedUtc": "2025-10-26T00:30:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "australian-spring-forward-skipped",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-10-04T02:30:00",
      "iana": "Australia/Sydney",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-10-03T16:30:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "unambiguous-utc-noon",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-06-15T12:00:00",
      "iana": "UTC",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-06-15T12:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "iana-normalization-us-pacific-alias",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-06-15T12:00:00",
      "iana": "US/Pacific",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-06-15T19:00:00Z",
      "expectedCanonicalIana": "America/Los_Angeles"
    },
    {
      "id": "iana-normalization-asia-saigon-renamed",
      "scheduledLocal": "2026-06-15T12:00:00",
      "iana": "Asia/Saigon",
      "expectedUtc": "2026-06-15T05:00:00Z",
      "expectedCanonicalIana": "Asia/Ho_Chi_Minh"
    }
  ],
  "$scalarComment": [
    "Per-temporal-type wire round-trip fixtures driving the TypeSpec-DTO temporal",
    "round-trip suites in BOTH languages (C# TemporalRoundTripTests +",
    "TS temporal-round-trip.test.ts). Each entry pins a wire string for one",
    "temporal scalar; both engines must materialize the equivalent domain value",
    "and re-emit the identical wire string. The 'kind' selects the NodaTime /",
    "Temporal pattern. 'wire' is the on-the-wire form the emitter produces",
    "(DateTimeOffset 'O' for instant/offset; offset-free ISO for plain-local;",
    "ISO-8601 P…T… for duration). 'offsetFree' marks values that MUST carry no",
    "offset (the no-invented-offset contract). If the two engines ever diverge on",
    "any entry, surface + acknowledge — DO NOT silently adjust."
  ],
  "scalarRoundTripFixtures": [
    {
      "id": "utc-instant-basic",
      "kind": "instant",
      "wire": "2026-05-27T14:30:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "utc-instant-year-boundary",
      "kind": "instant",
      "wire": "2025-12-31T23:59:59.9999999Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "utc-instant-subsecond-7digit",
      "kind": "instant",
      "wire": "2026-03-08T07:30:00.1234567Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "offset-datetime-minus-five",
      "kind": "offset",
      "wire": "2026-05-27T09:00:00-05:00",
      "expectedOffsetMinutes": -300
    },
    {
      "id": "offset-datetime-plus-ten-thirty",
      "kind": "offset",
      "wire": "2026-10-04T02:30:00+10:30",
      "expectedOffsetMinutes": 630
    },
    {
      "id": "plain-date-basic",
      "kind": "date",
      "wire": "2026-11-01",
      "offsetFree": true
    },
    {
      "id": "plain-date-leap-day",
      "kind": "date",
      "wire": "2024-02-29",
      "offsetFree": true
    },
    {
      "id": "plain-time-basic",
      "kind": "time",
      "wire": "09:42:00",
      "offsetFree": true
    },
    {
      "id": "plain-time-subsecond",
      "kind": "time",
      "wire": "23:59:59.9999999",
      "offsetFree": true
    },
    {
      "id": "plain-datetime-basic",
      "kind": "localDateTime",
      "wire": "2026-03-08T02:30:00",
      "offsetFree": true
    },
    {
      "id": "plain-datetime-leap-day",
      "kind": "localDateTime",
      "wire": "2024-02-29T12:00:00",
      "offsetFree": true
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-hours-minutes",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "PT1H30M"
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-days-and-time",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "P1DT2H3M4S"
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-seconds-only",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "PT45S"
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-subsecond-nanos",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "PT0.123456789S"
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-subsecond-half",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "PT0.5S"
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-subsecond-single-nano",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "PT0.000000001S"
    },
    {
      "id": "duration-hms-with-subsecond",
      "kind": "duration",
      "wire": "PT1H2M3.123456789S"
    }
  ]
}
